title: Informix DB: Status
agents: linux
catalog: app/informix
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This checks monitors instance status of
 Informix Database application.

 The check is OK if the instance status is in state
 initialization or online. It is WARN if the state is
 quiescent, recovery, backup, abort or single user and
 it goes CRIT if the state is shutdown or offline.

item:
 Name of the instance

inventory:
 One service is created for each instance.
